dxvk-native provides shared libraries installed to ${CURRENT_PACKAGES_DIR}/lib:

  libdxvk_dxgi.so
  libdxvk_d3d9.so      (feature: d3d9)
  libdxvk_d3d10core.so (feature: d3d10)
  libdxvk_d3d11.so     (feature: d3d11)

Pkg-config files are installed to ${CURRENT_PACKAGES_DIR}/lib/pkgconfig and
CMake config files to ${CURRENT_PACKAGES_DIR}/share/cmake/DXVK.

Runtime WSI selection
---------------------
Set the DXVK_WSI_DRIVER environment variable to choose the window-system
integration backend at runtime:

  export DXVK_WSI_DRIVER=SDL2   # or SDL3, GLFW

Link your application against the desired DXVK shared library and make sure
the library is on LD_LIBRARY_PATH (or in a standard search path).

CMake integration
-----------------

Modern CMake (find_package):
  find_package(DXVK REQUIRED)
  target_link_libraries(my_target PRIVATE DXVK::d3d11)
  # or link all modules: DXVK::DXVK

Available targets:
  - DXVK::d3d8
  - DXVK::d3d9
  - DXVK::d3d10core
  - DXVK::d3d11
  - DXVK::dxgi
  - DXVK::DXVK (interface library with all modules)

Pkg-config (legacy):
  find_package(PkgConfig REQUIRED)
  pkg_check_modules(DXVK_D3D11 REQUIRED IMPORTED_TARGET dxvk-d3d11)
  target_link_libraries(my_target PRIVATE PkgConfig::DXVK_D3D11)
